18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 63 =

20
00:01:34,620 --> 00:01:35,660
I asked someone

21
00:01:35,860 --> 00:01:37,180
to take the wine to a pharmacy owner.

22
00:01:38,220 --> 00:01:39,220
Soon, he figured out that

23
00:01:39,220 --> 00:01:40,900
there were a few kinds of philter in it.

24
00:01:42,020 --> 00:01:43,340
Whoever isn’t good at drinking

25
00:01:43,340 --> 00:01:44,420
may get in coma if she drinks too much.

26
00:01:45,020 --> 00:01:45,660
Mrs. Yang.

27
00:01:46,420 --> 00:01:48,100
What you did was insulting Princess

28
00:01:48,940 --> 00:01:50,260
and disrespecting the imperial family.

29
00:01:53,500 --> 00:01:54,180
Mrs. Yang.

30
00:01:55,220 --> 00:01:57,580
We can hide it from

31
00:01:57,580 --> 00:01:59,100
Princess, His Majesty and Her Highness.

32
00:01:59,620 --> 00:02:00,620
But you must swear

33
00:02:01,100 --> 00:02:03,060
you won’t do it ever again.

34
00:02:04,540 --> 00:02:05,580
I wanted to help Princess and Prince Consort

35
00:02:05,580 --> 00:02:07,180
with their consummation.

36
00:02:07,460 --> 00:02:08,940
His Majesty and Her Highness won’t blame me.

37
00:02:10,100 --> 00:02:11,180
If Liang Huaiji

38
00:02:11,180 --> 00:02:12,140
hadn’t interrupted,

39
00:02:12,340 --> 00:02:13,500
Princess and Prince Consort

40
00:02:13,500 --> 00:02:14,860
would have consummated their marriage.

41
00:02:16,540 --> 00:02:18,540
Princess is a tough girl.

42
00:02:19,260 --> 00:02:21,380
Once she knew she was drugged,

43
00:02:21,540 --> 00:02:23,300
she would never forgive Prince Consort.

44
00:02:24,060 --> 00:02:26,220
She might even kill herself as resistance.

45
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:28,620
If she died,

46
00:02:28,740 --> 00:02:29,900
could you or Prince Consort

47
00:02:29,900 --> 00:02:31,740
get out of it?

48
00:02:32,820 --> 00:02:35,060
Princess refused my son,

49
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:36,980
because she was too young to understand.

50
00:02:37,500 --> 00:02:38,660
Once she has the consummation

51
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:40,300
and enjoys it,

52
00:02:40,620 --> 00:02:42,500
she won’t reject my son.

53
00:02:43,620 --> 00:02:44,620
I don’t dare to say

54
00:02:44,780 --> 00:02:46,260
you’re wrong.

55
00:02:46,860 --> 00:02:48,460
But nothing comes with a guarantee.

56
00:02:49,100 --> 00:02:50,540
If she’s forced to have the consummation,

57
00:02:51,060 --> 00:02:52,420
there will be two consequences.

58
00:02:52,740 --> 00:02:54,660
First, she will accept Prince Consort,

59
00:02:55,340 --> 00:02:57,260
like you said.

60
00:02:57,580 --> 00:02:58,860
But she’s more likely

61
00:02:59,020 --> 00:03:00,020
to be angry

62
00:03:00,620 --> 00:03:02,540
and kill herself as resistance.

63
00:03:03,140 --> 00:03:04,900
As her servants,

64
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:06,300
our priority is

65
00:03:06,420 --> 00:03:08,540
to make her happy.

66
00:03:09,020 --> 00:03:10,860
We won’t let anyone

67
00:03:11,180 --> 00:03:12,180
hurt her.

68
00:03:13,100 --> 00:03:14,500
If you insist on going to the palace

69
00:03:14,540 --> 00:03:16,100
and tell His Majesty and Her Highness about it,

70
00:03:16,460 --> 00:03:17,900
we can’t stop you.

71
00:03:18,460 --> 00:03:19,660
But whatever happens,

72
00:03:20,020 --> 00:03:21,020
from today on,

73
00:03:21,540 --> 00:03:23,900
we’ll keep Princess company.

74
00:03:24,260 --> 00:03:26,700
Neither you or Prince Consort

75
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:28,820
can stay with her alone.

76
00:03:47,940 --> 00:03:48,820
Huaiji.

77
00:03:51,100 --> 00:03:51,780
Princess.

78
00:03:54,580 --> 00:03:55,620
Your face...

79
00:03:56,540 --> 00:03:57,780
How was it hurt?

80
00:04:01,820 --> 00:04:04,300
I bumped my face on the wall accidentally.

81
00:04:23,540 --> 00:04:24,980
Which wall?

82
00:04:28,540 --> 00:04:29,300
The stubbornness wall.

83
00:05:10,980 --> 00:05:11,780
Huaiji.

84
00:05:16,460 --> 00:05:17,820
You’re stuck.

85
00:05:34,260 --> 00:05:35,620
Stuck in my heart.

86
00:05:49,940 --> 00:05:51,100
I’m willing to

87
00:05:53,460 --> 00:05:54,860
be stuck there forever.

88
00:06:36,740 --> 00:06:37,740
Huaiji isn’t

89
00:06:38,580 --> 00:06:40,380
coming back before noon, is he?

90
00:06:42,220 --> 00:06:43,620
Mr. Liang has just left.

91
00:06:44,420 --> 00:06:45,940
I asked him to buy a lot of things.

92
00:06:46,260 --> 00:06:47,620
To buy everything on the list,

93
00:06:48,580 --> 00:06:51,180
he may not even be back in the afternoon.

94
00:07:07,820 --> 00:07:08,620
Mrs. Yang.

95
00:07:10,420 --> 00:07:11,900
I was too careless.

96
00:07:13,460 --> 00:07:15,340
A bad guy broke into my mansion

97
00:07:16,660 --> 00:07:18,540
and just ransacked

98
00:07:19,420 --> 00:07:20,460
your bedroom.

99
00:07:29,260 --> 00:07:30,500
But don’t worry.

100
00:07:31,980 --> 00:07:32,740
From now on,

101
00:07:33,460 --> 00:07:34,500
I’ll ask servants

102
00:07:35,180 --> 00:07:36,100
to guard in your yard

103
00:07:36,100 --> 00:07:38,380
day and night in shifts.

104
00:07:40,580 --> 00:07:42,940
They will see clearly

105
00:07:43,580 --> 00:07:44,980
who come and go.

106
00:07:47,180 --> 00:07:48,980
They’ll let nobody suspicious in,

107
00:07:50,060 --> 00:07:50,900
or let anyone out

108
00:07:50,900 --> 00:07:52,260
if I don’t trust him.

109
00:07:56,580 --> 00:07:58,300
If someone else still wants to

110
00:07:59,020 --> 00:08:00,140
hurt people,

111
00:08:03,380 --> 00:08:04,580
just like this bitchy maid.

112
00:08:10,260 --> 00:08:11,900
I won’t let her go like I did this time.

113
00:08:14,540 --> 00:08:16,060
I’ll kill her

114
00:08:17,740 --> 00:08:18,820
and skin her.

115
00:08:43,300 --> 00:08:44,060
Mother.

116
00:08:46,020 --> 00:08:47,300
You blame me for drugging her?

117
00:08:53,700 --> 00:08:55,060
If I didn’t drug her,

118
00:08:56,020 --> 00:08:57,100
you had to wait.

119
00:08:57,780 --> 00:08:58,620
Would she...

120
00:08:58,860 --> 00:09:00,540
Would she look back at you?

121
00:09:02,060 --> 00:09:02,900
No.

122
00:09:03,340 --> 00:09:04,980
She won’t!

123
00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:08,340
In her eyes,

124
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:11,700
she only cares for that eunuch!

125
00:09:12,940 --> 00:09:14,380
With him around,

126
00:09:15,420 --> 00:09:16,460
she will never

127
00:09:16,460 --> 00:09:17,780
look at you.

128
00:09:17,980 --> 00:09:18,900
Don’t you know?

129
00:09:20,780 --> 00:09:23,420
You good-for-nothing son!

130
00:09:23,940 --> 00:09:26,500
What a loser! Loser!

131
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:46,820
Huaiji.

132
00:09:58,940 --> 00:09:59,700
Princess.

133
00:10:00,940 --> 00:10:01,860
It’s getting late.

134
00:10:02,380 --> 00:10:03,740
Go back to sleep early.

135
00:10:05,180 --> 00:10:06,300
I can’t fall asleep.

136
00:10:06,700 --> 00:10:07,940
I want to talk with you.

137
00:10:10,820 --> 00:10:11,860
If you want a talk,

138
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:13,340
we can do it tomorrow.

139
00:10:33,140 --> 00:10:34,060
Mr. Liang.

140
00:10:35,580 --> 00:10:38,300
Princess sits outside and refuses to go back.

141
00:10:52,180 --> 00:10:53,020
Huaiji.

142
00:10:54,940 --> 00:10:55,780
I’m cold.

143
00:11:00,740 --> 00:11:01,780
Hold her to my room, then.

144
00:11:06,180 --> 00:11:06,940
Princess, come.

145
00:11:26,740 --> 00:11:27,940
Do you have wine?

146
00:11:30,340 --> 00:11:31,140
It’s too late.

147
00:11:31,660 --> 00:11:32,820
I’ll drink with you tomorrow.

148
00:11:36,220 --> 00:11:39,300
Brother, I’m so cold.

149
00:12:08,540 --> 00:12:10,460
Go make some hangover-cure soup for Princess.

150
00:12:29,300 --> 00:12:30,860
Why do I need that?

151
00:12:33,020 --> 00:12:35,700
It’s said that wine cures sorrow.

152
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:38,340
If I become sober,

153
00:12:39,140 --> 00:12:40,580
isn’t sorrow back again?

154
00:12:43,740 --> 00:12:44,620
In this world,

155
00:12:45,820 --> 00:12:47,220
no wine can really cure sorrow.

156
00:12:49,420 --> 00:12:50,380
When you drown your sorrows in wine,

157
00:12:51,140 --> 00:12:52,260
you just want to get hammered

158
00:12:52,820 --> 00:12:54,740
and forget your sorrow for a moment.

159
00:12:58,700 --> 00:13:00,820
It’s not bad

160
00:13:01,700 --> 00:13:02,540
when I can forget it for a moment.

161
00:13:05,140 --> 00:13:06,100
I have a lot of things

162
00:13:06,100 --> 00:13:07,580
to forget.

163
00:13:23,660 --> 00:13:24,700
Hope this cup of wine will

164
00:13:25,940 --> 00:13:26,980
make me forget

165
00:13:27,900 --> 00:13:28,900
everything about

166
00:13:28,900 --> 00:13:30,060
Li Wei and his mother.

167
00:13:50,660 --> 00:13:51,380
What about you?

168
00:13:53,460 --> 00:13:54,300
You must have something

169
00:13:54,300 --> 00:13:55,580
that you want to forget.

170
00:14:14,260 --> 00:14:15,180
Hope this cup of wine

171
00:14:17,140 --> 00:14:18,500
will let me forget

172
00:14:19,500 --> 00:14:21,980
all the unhappy memories.

173
00:14:26,460 --> 00:14:27,460
What are they?

174
00:14:33,740 --> 00:14:34,580
You said

175
00:14:36,340 --> 00:14:37,500
you were from a poor family.

176
00:14:39,780 --> 00:14:41,540
Everyone can be somewhat poor.

177
00:14:43,780 --> 00:14:44,700
When I was little,

178
00:14:45,740 --> 00:14:47,260
I thought I was poor

179
00:14:48,340 --> 00:14:49,940
because I couldn’t go out for fun.

180
00:14:54,260 --> 00:14:55,420
Later I knew

181
00:14:57,100 --> 00:14:58,580
I was even poorer.

182
00:15:02,940 --> 00:15:04,700
Compared to a girl like Qiuhe,

183
00:15:07,580 --> 00:15:09,060
I’m so poor.

184
00:15:23,340 --> 00:15:24,420
Hope this cup of wine

185
00:15:25,540 --> 00:15:26,660
can make me forget

186
00:15:27,460 --> 00:15:28,980
I’m a princess.

187
00:15:31,260 --> 00:15:32,900
It’ll be for good and all.

188
00:15:34,980 --> 00:15:36,420
Because all my sorrows

189
00:15:37,380 --> 00:15:40,060
are resulted from my identity.

190
00:16:00,580 --> 00:16:01,900
If I were not a princess,

191
00:16:04,060 --> 00:16:05,220
what else could I be?

192
00:16:10,820 --> 00:16:11,860
I’d like to be

193
00:16:13,380 --> 00:16:14,700
a lotus.

194
00:16:18,060 --> 00:16:19,820
I could blossom on the river every year,

195
00:16:21,620 --> 00:16:22,940
watching the receding boats

196
00:16:24,740 --> 00:16:26,140
and looking at wandering clouds.

197
00:16:28,820 --> 00:16:29,980
I would be free.

198
00:16:33,540 --> 00:16:34,540
Sounds nice.

199
00:16:40,580 --> 00:16:41,380
Stop laughing.

200
00:16:42,300 --> 00:16:43,220
Tell me.

201
00:16:44,300 --> 00:16:45,340
What do you want to be?

202
00:16:49,100 --> 00:16:50,220
If you were a lotus,

203
00:16:51,940 --> 00:16:52,860
I wanted to be

204
00:16:53,940 --> 00:16:55,860
the waves below your leaves.

205
00:16:58,300 --> 00:16:58,980
In this way,

206
00:16:59,380 --> 00:17:01,180
we could stay with each other

207
00:17:01,780 --> 00:17:03,780
and communicate for years.

208
00:17:07,940 --> 00:17:08,820
Fill your cup.

209
00:17:11,180 --> 00:17:13,740
Go on drinking and talking.

210
00:17:17,140 --> 00:17:18,820
Tell me what you want to forget.

211
00:17:31,580 --> 00:17:32,820
Except what I just said,

212
00:17:34,580 --> 00:17:35,540
I don’t have

213
00:17:36,580 --> 00:17:37,460
any other important things

214
00:17:37,460 --> 00:17:38,900
to forget.

215
00:17:44,580 --> 00:17:45,860
If you insist,

216
00:17:47,180 --> 00:17:48,740
I’ll change it into a wish.

217
00:17:50,620 --> 00:17:51,660
What wish?

218
00:18:04,380 --> 00:18:05,300
I wish

219
00:18:08,180 --> 00:18:09,140
however hard we wanted to

220
00:18:10,340 --> 00:18:12,180
modify our memories,

221
00:18:15,180 --> 00:18:16,540
we would still stay

222
00:18:16,540 --> 00:18:17,540
in each other’s life.

223
00:18:24,780 --> 00:18:25,660
I remember...

224
00:18:28,940 --> 00:18:29,980
I remember everything that happened

225
00:18:29,980 --> 00:18:31,460
when I was with you.

226
00:18:35,300 --> 00:18:36,780
I remember your sorrows,

227
00:18:38,500 --> 00:18:39,540
your smiles

228
00:18:41,660 --> 00:18:43,420
and everything you said to me

229
00:18:46,900 --> 00:18:47,580
and...

230
00:18:49,740 --> 00:18:51,100
and all bruises you had

231
00:18:52,260 --> 00:18:53,500
because of me.

232
00:19:09,260 --> 00:19:10,020
Who’s there?

233
00:19:20,380 --> 00:19:21,220
Mr. Liang.

234
00:19:21,820 --> 00:19:23,020
Now,

235
00:19:23,620 --> 00:19:24,940
what can you argue?

236
00:19:27,460 --> 00:19:28,860
You were peeping at us?

237
00:19:29,820 --> 00:19:32,100
What? I can’t?

238
00:19:33,180 --> 00:19:34,340
Since you dare to

239
00:19:34,340 --> 00:19:35,380
do such a shameless thing,

240
00:19:35,620 --> 00:19:36,780
why can’t I look at you?

241
00:19:37,860 --> 00:19:38,860
How dare you!

242
00:19:39,380 --> 00:19:40,260
How dirty

243
00:19:40,260 --> 00:19:41,180
you are talking!

244
00:19:42,820 --> 00:19:44,700
Am I talking dirty?

245
00:19:45,020 --> 00:19:46,740
Or you’re doing dirty?

246
00:19:47,980 --> 00:19:48,980
Princess, could you

247
00:19:48,980 --> 00:19:50,060
tell your servants

248
00:19:50,900 --> 00:19:52,060
what you were doing with Mr. Liang

249
00:19:52,580 --> 00:19:54,420
in this room?

250
00:19:57,580 --> 00:19:58,180
Li Wei.

251
00:19:58,700 --> 00:19:59,660
Come over.

252
00:20:01,020 --> 00:20:02,100
Take him away

253
00:20:02,540 --> 00:20:03,940
and let His Majesty punish him tomorrow.

254
00:20:07,220 --> 00:20:08,180
How dare you!

255
00:20:09,780 --> 00:20:10,740
What are you waiting for?

256
00:20:11,100 --> 00:20:12,380
Until they humiliate you

257
00:20:12,380 --> 00:20:13,820
and cuckold you?

258
00:20:19,100 --> 00:20:20,460
Come if you want to die.

259
00:20:23,740 --> 00:20:25,780
If you dare to hurt Huaiji,

260
00:20:26,500 --> 00:20:27,100
I’ll...

261
00:20:27,100 --> 00:20:28,060
You’ll go to the palace

262
00:20:28,220 --> 00:20:29,380
and complain about me to His Majesty

263
00:20:29,860 --> 00:20:31,700
for bullying you and drugging you?

264
00:20:33,620 --> 00:20:34,580
Do you think

265
00:20:34,780 --> 00:20:35,620
it’s a great sin

266
00:20:35,620 --> 00:20:36,820
in His Majesty’s eyes?

267
00:20:37,860 --> 00:20:39,780
Since you married my son,

268
00:20:40,340 --> 00:20:42,140
His Majesty has been expecting you
to consummate your marriage.

269
00:20:42,820 --> 00:20:44,340
What’s wrong with it

270
00:20:44,340 --> 00:20:45,180
when I taught you?

271
00:20:46,020 --> 00:20:47,660
After you consummate your marriage,

272
00:20:47,900 --> 00:20:48,940
you’ll understand.

273
00:20:49,780 --> 00:20:51,100
Ask them to take him down.

274
00:20:53,660 --> 00:20:55,100
Mother. Mother.

275
00:20:55,380 --> 00:20:56,300
You bit...

276
00:20:56,300 --> 00:20:56,900
Princess.

277
00:20:56,900 --> 00:20:58,020
You bitch!

278
00:20:58,020 --> 00:20:58,660
Princess.

279
00:20:58,900 --> 00:21:00,420
Princess, calm down.

280
00:21:00,540 --> 00:21:01,660
Calm down!

281
00:21:02,180 --> 00:21:02,940
Princess.

282
00:21:03,340 --> 00:21:04,500
Princess. Princess.

283
00:21:04,500 --> 00:21:05,540
Why do I have

284
00:21:06,140 --> 00:21:09,700
such a cowardly son?

285
00:21:10,900 --> 00:21:12,940
What a coward!

286
00:21:14,460 --> 00:21:15,500
When you have a wife...

287
00:21:15,500 --> 00:21:16,540
Why did you hit my mother?

288
00:21:16,900 --> 00:21:17,820
Why?

289
00:21:18,740 --> 00:21:21,180
But he still defends her.

290
00:21:22,020 --> 00:21:23,420
He still

291
00:21:23,460 --> 00:21:25,460
allows her and that eunuch

292
00:21:25,940 --> 00:21:28,660
to humiliate him.

293
00:21:29,260 --> 00:21:31,260
He doesn’t even snort.

294
00:21:33,420 --> 00:21:34,340
Now,

295
00:21:35,740 --> 00:21:38,420
she even dared to hit your mother.

296
00:21:41,340 --> 00:21:44,060
What wrong have I done?

297
00:21:45,980 --> 00:21:47,380
If I knew it,

298
00:21:48,100 --> 00:21:49,940
I would rather have no son

299
00:21:49,940 --> 00:21:52,580
than have you.

300
00:22:13,940 --> 00:22:14,660
Princess.

301
00:22:14,660 --> 00:22:15,460
Huaiji.

302
00:22:17,540 --> 00:22:19,300
Fine.

303
00:22:19,740 --> 00:22:20,740
I’m taking you back.

304
00:22:22,700 --> 00:22:23,540
Where?

305
00:22:24,700 --> 00:22:25,660
Your bedroom.

306
00:22:27,260 --> 00:22:28,220
I’m going home.

307
00:22:29,700 --> 00:22:30,540
Home?

308
00:22:31,700 --> 00:22:32,700
I’m going back to the palace.

309
00:22:36,700 --> 00:22:37,380
Princess.

310
00:22:37,940 --> 00:22:39,500
All gates of the palace have been closed.

311
00:22:40,380 --> 00:22:41,860
I’m going back to the palace.

312
00:22:46,300 --> 00:22:47,060
Princess.

313
00:22:47,540 --> 00:22:48,380
It’s raining.

314
00:22:48,860 --> 00:22:50,300
Why don’t we go tomorrow...

315
00:22:51,300 --> 00:22:52,100
Huaiji.

316
00:22:57,140 --> 00:22:58,140
Take me back home.

317
00:22:59,940 --> 00:23:00,940
I’m going out.

318
00:23:01,700 --> 00:23:03,180
I don’t want to be stuck here.

319
00:23:09,260 --> 00:23:10,020
Okay.

320
00:23:11,100 --> 00:23:12,020
I’m taking you back to the palace.

321
00:23:40,020 --> 00:23:40,900
Princess!

322
00:23:42,300 --> 00:23:43,140
Princess!

323
00:23:43,940 --> 00:23:44,940
Princess!

324
00:23:47,460 --> 00:23:48,460
Huirou!

325
00:23:50,220 --> 00:23:51,140
Huirou!

326
00:23:53,980 --> 00:23:54,900
Huirou!

327
00:23:55,696 --> 00:23:56,686
Huirou!

328
00:23:56,820 --> 00:23:57,580
Go!

329
00:23:59,740 --> 00:24:00,660
Hurry!

330
00:24:05,180 --> 00:24:06,700
If I stay for one more minute,

331
00:24:08,860 --> 00:24:10,180
I’m going to die.

332
00:24:20,340 --> 00:24:22,020
Your Majesty, what do you want?

333
00:24:45,420 --> 00:24:47,980
Shall I close the door? It’s cold out there.

334
00:24:58,860 --> 00:24:59,940
Your Majesty, you don’t feel well?

335
00:25:00,340 --> 00:25:01,300
I’ll go get the Physician.

336
00:25:03,140 --> 00:25:04,260
Give me the medicine.

337
00:25:32,380 --> 00:25:33,900
Since they began to heal me,

338
00:25:33,900 --> 00:25:35,300
they always gave the same medicine.

339
00:25:36,020 --> 00:25:38,180
Don’t bother them in the middle of night.

340
00:25:39,100 --> 00:25:40,420
I don’t want that, either.

341
00:25:50,860 --> 00:25:52,660
I dreamed of Zuixinglai.

342
00:25:56,180 --> 00:25:57,740
He was reciting a poem

343
00:25:59,780 --> 00:26:01,460
with a poor fluency.

344
00:26:02,700 --> 00:26:05,780
He also took a glance at Huirou.

345
00:26:09,980 --> 00:26:11,820
But Huirou didn’t know it, either.

346
00:26:13,620 --> 00:26:15,900
She used to read and study

347
00:26:15,900 --> 00:26:17,220
only because I asked her to.

348
00:26:20,220 --> 00:26:21,380
Zuixinglai was

349
00:26:23,220 --> 00:26:24,980
more docile than his sister.

350
00:26:26,420 --> 00:26:29,140
He was clever and obedient.

351
00:26:31,340 --> 00:26:32,900
Old maids often said

352
00:26:34,100 --> 00:26:35,540
he was like the young me.

353
00:26:38,380 --> 00:26:39,380
I thought about it.

354
00:26:40,780 --> 00:26:42,460
He didn’t lack

355
00:26:44,380 --> 00:26:45,700
what I lacked in my childhood.

356
00:26:47,660 --> 00:26:48,780
He used to have everything.

357
00:26:50,060 --> 00:26:52,100
His father, mother.

358
00:26:52,820 --> 00:26:54,540
legal mother and elder sister

359
00:26:56,460 --> 00:26:57,540
all loved him.

360
00:27:16,620 --> 00:27:17,660
Zuixinglai...

361
00:27:20,300 --> 00:27:21,620
Why was he gone?

362
00:27:29,140 --> 00:27:29,780
Maybe...

363
00:27:30,260 --> 00:27:31,220
everyone has to

364
00:27:31,220 --> 00:27:32,660
suffer in his life.

365
00:27:33,620 --> 00:27:36,340
The Second Prince was the loveliest boy.

366
00:27:36,940 --> 00:27:39,020
Everyone loved him and spoilt him.

367
00:27:40,540 --> 00:27:41,300
At last,

368
00:27:41,700 --> 00:27:42,860
the Heaven didn’t want him

369
00:27:42,860 --> 00:27:44,140
to suffer in the world.

370
00:28:11,060 --> 00:28:11,940
Princess!

371
00:28:18,020 --> 00:28:19,300
Huirou!

372
00:28:19,620 --> 00:28:20,660
Why?

373
00:28:21,300 --> 00:28:22,740
Why could you be like this?

374
00:28:23,100 --> 00:28:24,500
Why?

375
00:28:37,700 --> 00:28:38,500
Huirou.

376
00:29:06,220 --> 00:29:12,300
= Way of Man =

377
00:29:22,620 --> 00:29:29,580
= My... =

378
00:29:29,580 --> 00:29:35,060
= My son =

379
00:29:41,940 --> 00:29:42,740
Who is that?

380
00:29:43,980 --> 00:29:44,660
Stop!

381
00:29:45,460 --> 00:29:46,580
How dare you break in?

382
00:29:46,780 --> 00:29:47,700
Are you tired of living?

383
00:29:49,860 --> 00:29:50,620
Stop!

384
00:29:53,300 --> 00:29:54,020
Princess?

385
00:29:54,420 --> 00:29:55,300
Who the hell are you?

386
00:29:55,300 --> 00:29:55,780
Father.

387
00:29:55,780 --> 00:29:56,420
Go back.

388
00:29:58,020 --> 00:29:58,660
Go back.

389
00:29:58,980 --> 00:30:00,340
Stop, or you’ll be sorry.

390
00:30:00,780 --> 00:30:01,500
Stop!

391
00:30:01,500 --> 00:30:02,180
Stop!

392
00:30:02,180 --> 00:30:02,940
Wait. Wait.

393
00:30:03,380 --> 00:30:04,220
- Father. Your Highness. - I recognize him.

394
00:30:04,380 --> 00:30:06,260
- He’s Mr. Liang Huaiji. - Father. Your Highness.

395
00:30:06,420 --> 00:30:07,460
Mr. Liang Huaiji?

396
00:30:07,620 --> 00:30:09,460
- Open the gate and let me go home.
- Yes. Liang Huaiji.

397
00:30:10,100 --> 00:30:10,900
Who is she then?

398
00:30:11,220 --> 00:30:12,140
Father.

399
00:30:13,220 --> 00:30:14,060
Princess Fukang.

400
00:30:14,300 --> 00:30:15,260
Your Highness.

401
00:30:16,820 --> 00:30:18,980
Open the gate and let me go home.

402
00:31:02,900 --> 00:31:05,220
Your Majesty, go to sleep.

403
00:31:22,020 --> 00:31:24,380
Do you remember how Zuixinglai looked?

404
00:31:31,020 --> 00:31:34,140
He looked cute

405
00:31:34,980 --> 00:31:35,940
and clever,

406
00:31:36,860 --> 00:31:37,500
and...

407
00:31:45,380 --> 00:31:46,060
Your Majesty.

408
00:31:47,780 --> 00:31:48,860
Is someone coming?

409
00:31:55,300 --> 00:31:56,900
Your Majesty, no one is coming.

410
00:31:57,700 --> 00:31:58,700
It’s almost midnight.

411
00:32:01,380 --> 00:32:02,780
Let me get you to sleep?

412
00:32:10,460 --> 00:32:12,060
I’m feeling unsettled.

413
00:32:14,340 --> 00:32:15,380
These days,

414
00:32:16,860 --> 00:32:18,660
I always think of Zuixinglai.

415
00:32:19,620 --> 00:32:21,540
But I can’t see his face clearly.

416
00:32:24,540 --> 00:32:26,540
I think of Huirou

417
00:32:27,220 --> 00:32:29,100
when she ate the candied fruits privately.

418
00:32:30,300 --> 00:32:31,340
I remember it

419
00:32:33,580 --> 00:32:34,780
when she told me

420
00:32:37,460 --> 00:32:39,340
if I killed Cao Ping,

421
00:32:41,060 --> 00:32:43,620
she would kill my only daughter.

422
00:32:53,100 --> 00:32:53,780
Your Majesty.

423
00:32:54,820 --> 00:32:56,220
You’re too tired

424
00:32:57,020 --> 00:32:58,260
and you miss the Second Prince too much.

425
00:33:00,660 --> 00:33:01,420
Your Majesty.

426
00:33:02,100 --> 00:33:04,100
Madam Dong and Madam Zhou

427
00:33:04,580 --> 00:33:05,820
are still young.

428
00:33:06,540 --> 00:33:07,740
They will give birth to sons

429
00:33:08,020 --> 00:33:09,220
for you.

430
00:33:11,180 --> 00:33:13,060
Princess Fukang is the most obedient.

431
00:33:13,900 --> 00:33:15,020
You love her the most.

432
00:33:15,900 --> 00:33:17,980
Why do you always remember

433
00:33:19,540 --> 00:33:21,620
what she said when she was angry?

434
00:33:26,140 --> 00:33:27,860
I’m not afraid if she hates me.

435
00:33:30,100 --> 00:33:32,620
But I’m afraid she’ll split hairs.

436
00:33:41,220 --> 00:33:43,060
Her Highness asks to see you for emergency.

437
00:35:30,380 --> 00:35:31,140
Your Majesty.

438
00:35:42,140 --> 00:35:43,020
Father.

439
00:35:44,860 --> 00:35:46,540
Stand up. Stand up.

440
00:36:20,100 --> 00:36:21,220
What happened?

441
00:36:22,220 --> 00:36:22,940
Huirou.

442
00:36:23,420 --> 00:36:24,980
Tell me what happened.

443
00:36:28,220 --> 00:36:30,220
Tell me what happened.

444
00:36:31,820 --> 00:36:32,740
Mother.

445
00:36:35,660 --> 00:36:36,900
Please beg father

446
00:36:37,180 --> 00:36:38,380
to keep me.

447
00:36:39,020 --> 00:36:40,100
Please keep me

448
00:36:41,100 --> 00:36:42,260
in the palace.

449
00:36:45,820 --> 00:36:46,740
I’m begging you.

450
00:36:48,340 --> 00:36:50,020
If...if there’s no space

451
00:36:50,100 --> 00:36:51,340
for me,

452
00:36:52,980 --> 00:36:53,780
father,

453
00:36:54,540 --> 00:36:55,660
please execute me.

454
00:36:55,660 --> 00:36:56,540
Nonsense!

455
00:37:01,340 --> 00:37:02,420
Father.

456
00:37:07,420 --> 00:37:08,180
Father.

457
00:37:11,140 --> 00:37:12,340
Whenever I think of Li Wei,

458
00:37:13,780 --> 00:37:14,740
I...

459
00:37:15,180 --> 00:37:16,460
I can’t stay with him

460
00:37:16,460 --> 00:37:17,340
for even one more second.

461
00:37:18,140 --> 00:37:19,180
Whenever I think of him,

462
00:37:19,420 --> 00:37:21,260
I remember how he raised his hand to slap me.

463
00:37:25,220 --> 00:37:26,100
Slapped you?

464
00:37:27,020 --> 00:37:28,420
How dared he slap you!

465
00:37:28,860 --> 00:37:30,020
Where were you hurt?

466
00:37:30,540 --> 00:37:32,700
Huirou, where were you hurt?

467
00:37:34,380 --> 00:37:35,500
Damn it!

468
00:37:36,020 --> 00:37:37,180
How dared him!

469
00:37:37,820 --> 00:37:38,780
I’m going to kill him!

470
00:37:39,020 --> 00:37:39,860
Your Majesty.

471
00:37:41,700 --> 00:37:42,780
Father.

472
00:37:42,780 --> 00:37:44,700
When Huirou did her homework poorly

473
00:37:44,700 --> 00:37:45,780
or she was naughty,

474
00:37:46,620 --> 00:37:47,820
you and Her Highness

475
00:37:47,980 --> 00:37:49,500
only taught her a lesson

476
00:37:49,620 --> 00:37:50,700
or instructed her.

477
00:37:50,700 --> 00:37:51,860
Not to mention you never slapped her,

478
00:37:51,980 --> 00:37:53,860
you haven’t even said any harsh words.

479
00:38:01,340 --> 00:38:02,100
Come with me.

480
00:38:06,860 --> 00:38:07,740
Your Highness.

481
00:38:10,620 --> 00:38:11,780
What are you going to do with Huaiji?

482
00:38:15,940 --> 00:38:16,860
It’s not his fault.

483
00:38:18,780 --> 00:38:19,700
It’s not his fault.

484
00:38:20,420 --> 00:38:21,220
It’s my fault.

485
00:38:22,020 --> 00:38:23,380
I pestered him.

486
00:38:25,380 --> 00:38:27,700
Punish me if you insist.

487
00:38:32,940 --> 00:38:35,220
Huirou, what happened?

488
00:38:40,820 --> 00:38:42,860
What happened to her

489
00:38:42,860 --> 00:38:43,820
that made her so scared?

490
00:39:14,820 --> 00:39:15,700
Father.

491
00:39:29,340 --> 00:39:30,180
Huirou.

492
00:39:32,540 --> 00:39:34,300
Go back with your mother for some rest.

493
00:39:37,700 --> 00:39:39,380
Huirou. Go with me.

494
00:39:39,540 --> 00:39:40,420
Go.

495
00:39:40,900 --> 00:39:41,780
Huaiji.

496
00:39:41,780 --> 00:39:42,780
Father.

497
00:39:46,740 --> 00:39:47,460
Father.

498
00:39:49,380 --> 00:39:50,740
Li Wei and his mother

499
00:39:51,300 --> 00:39:52,180
drugged me

500
00:39:53,300 --> 00:39:54,380
and humiliated me.

501
00:39:55,380 --> 00:39:56,700
Without Huaiji,

502
00:39:57,500 --> 00:39:59,220
I would have died.

503
00:39:59,540 --> 00:40:02,060
I forced him to drink with me.

504
00:40:02,580 --> 00:40:03,420
Ren Shouzhong!

505
00:40:06,540 --> 00:40:07,300
Your Majesty.

506
00:40:08,180 --> 00:40:09,500
Escort Madam Miao and Huirou

507
00:40:09,500 --> 00:40:10,780
to Pavilion of Phoenix.

508
00:40:11,380 --> 00:40:12,100
Aye.

509
00:40:12,860 --> 00:40:13,500
Father!

510
00:40:13,500 --> 00:40:14,260
Huirou!

511
00:40:18,100 --> 00:40:19,260
When you’re fine,

512
00:40:20,700 --> 00:40:22,420
those around you will be fine, too.

513
00:40:23,580 --> 00:40:25,220
If something is wrong with you,

514
00:40:26,060 --> 00:40:27,700
I’ll punish them severely.

515
00:40:27,700 --> 00:40:28,820
None of them will get away.

516
00:40:35,060 --> 00:40:35,780
Huirou, go.

517
00:40:36,700 --> 00:40:37,420
Go.

518
00:40:37,700 --> 00:40:39,500
Let’s go. Hurry.

519
00:40:41,500 --> 00:40:42,340
Get up.

520
00:41:08,220 --> 00:41:09,140
Mother.

521
00:41:11,620 --> 00:41:13,020
Without Huaiji,

522
00:41:15,140 --> 00:41:16,820
I would have died.

523
00:41:22,740 --> 00:41:23,740
I know.

524
00:41:25,940 --> 00:41:27,700
Huaiji is a good boy.

525
00:41:43,060 --> 00:41:50,060
♪ Memory is the breath of deep sleep ♪

526
00:41:50,620 --> 00:41:57,500
♪ It emerges in every crevice ♪

527
00:41:57,980 --> 00:42:04,340
♪ Shallow dreams are like
copper bells under eaves ♪

528
00:42:04,780 --> 00:42:11,540
♪ Woken up when the wind blows ♪

529
00:42:12,780 --> 00:42:19,580
♪ Fate is predetermined ♪

530
00:42:20,180 --> 00:42:26,940
♪ Struggle to break out of it ♪

531
00:42:27,500 --> 00:42:34,540
♪ Who will battle fate with me ♪

532
00:42:34,540 --> 00:42:41,340
♪ Regardless of the ending ♪

533
00:42:46,220 --> 00:42:49,740
♪ Peach branches shake in the spring breeze ♪

534
00:42:49,940 --> 00:42:53,540
♪ Walls sigh, the wind is silent ♪

535
00:42:53,540 --> 00:42:56,740
♪ The boy beside the wall is unaware of it ♪

536
00:42:56,740 --> 00:43:01,140
♪ He plays with the butterfly, gathering honey ♪

537
00:43:01,140 --> 00:43:04,860
♪ Peach blossoms tell a love story ♪

538
00:43:04,860 --> 00:43:08,420
♪ About a couple who lives happily ♪

539
00:43:08,420 --> 00:43:12,140
♪ Unluckily deep love comes to nowhere ♪

540
00:43:12,140 --> 00:43:17,900
♪ All fated,
drawing Double Happiness in autumn ♪

